<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #1E2E82;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content h1 {
            color: #c78444;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #333333;
        }
        .verify-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #040543;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #1E2E82;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer img {
            margin: 0 5px;
            max-width: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Thanks for Signing Up!</h1>
            <p>Hi, <%= name %></p>
            <p>You're almost ready to get started. Please click on the button below to verify your email address and enjoy exclusive cleaning services with us!</p>
            <a href="<%= verifyUrl %>" style="color: white" class="verify-button">Verify Your Email</a>
            <p>Thanks,<br>The Company Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Get in touch</p>
            <div>
                <a href="#"><img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS5ICC-lsJhMbtaUOMtD0zGKGowxMdmIs3iUfXtk3T3Mw&s" alt="Facebook"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6f/Logo_of_Twitter.svg/512px-Logo_of_Twitter.svg.png?20220821125553" alt="Twitter"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e7/Instagram_logo_2016.svg/2048px-Instagram_logo_2016.svg.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
            </div>
            <p>Copyrights Â© Company All Rights Reserved</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
